English:
Log E105-014 

Date:		January 31st 2053 
Patient:		Employee E105 (Edgar Soweta) 
Att. Phys:	Dr. August Teale B023 

 //HearSay auto-transcript begins// 

 

Teale 

Good morning Edgar. 

Teale 

Not talking today? 

Teale 

I spoke to the pharmacy. 

E105 

[inaudible] 

Teale 

You haven’t collected your prescription. 

E105 

[inaudible] 

Teale 

You’ll need to speak up Edgar. 

E105 

I don’t want pills. 

Teale 

Why not? 

E105 

Too foggy. 

Teale 

We can lower the dose. 

Teale 

It’s important that you take the pills Edgar. These… hallucinations-- 

E105 

They’re not hallucinations. 

Teale 

Forgive me. These… visions cause you a lot of distress. 

E105 

No pills. 

Teale 

Edgar-- 

E105 

No pills. 

Teale 

If you are unwilling to help yourself, I can’t in good conscience allow you to return to the mine. 

E105 

Okay. 

Teale 

You don’t want to work? 

E105 

I’m not taking any more pills. 

Teale 

Very well. I’ll let operations know that you’re on medical leave until further notice. I don’t think we should wait until next week for your next session. Stop by tomorrow, okay? 

Teale 

HearSay off. 

 
//HearSay auto-transcript ends//
